      "date": "2016-05-13 20:47:32.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1: Code-Review-1\n\nI'm not sure I understand the requirement for this patch.  Specifying \"brw_size=16M\" and \"max_pages_per_rpc=\"4M\" should work properly, unless the recent landing of http://review.whamcloud.com/16930 has broken this?  In that case, the 16930 patch should be reverted or fixed.\n\nOtherwise, this is a userspace-visible change will break existing configurations that are using these parameters with the unit suffix.",
