      "message": "Patch Set 1: Verified+1\n\nTests uploaded by Onyx Autotest from onyx-60vm1 for review-dne-part-1 received by maloo, run on CentOS Linux 7/x86_64: (https://testing.hpdd.intel.com/test_sessions/165e7264-1a3a-11e6-9e5d-5254006e85c2). Ran 7 tests. No failures.",
